727591f-a.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - 41st Avenue
727591f-a.text:
Northern Boulevard, west side, between 4lst Avenue and
40th Road, showing the Queensborough Stadium. Northern
Boulevard is in the upper right hand corner and shows the
I.R.T.-B.M.T. elevated structure thereon, the view being
northwestward from 41st Avenue.
March 23, 1932
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr
